	(1, 'Hamilton vows to \'not give up\' this season', 'Lewis Hamilton thanks his supporters and shares his hopes of wanting to improve this season.', 'https://www.espn.com/video/clip?id=44869101', 'https://a.espncdn.com/media/motion/2025/0426/dm_250426_COM_F1_News_Hamilton_vows_to_not_give_up_this_season_20250426_GLOBAL/dm_250426_COM_F1_News_Hamilton_vows_to_not_give_up_this_season_20250426_GLOBAL.jpg', 'Lewis Hamilton thanks his supporters and shares his hopes of wanting to improve this season.', '', 324, 576, '2025-04-28 00:18:43', 'c6fa04d430d38'),
	(2, 'Carlos Sainz: Madrid\'s Madring \'can be best circuit in the world\'', 'Madrid\'s Madring Formula 1 circuit can host the best race on the calendar when it debuts next season, according to home driver Carlos Sainz.', 'https://www.espn.co.uk/f1/story/_/id/44852960/carlos-sainz-madrid-madring-best-circuit-world', 'https://a.espncdn.com/photo/2025/0425/r1483842_1296x729_16-9.jpg', '', 'Carlos Sainz of Spain and Williams points at a model of the Formula 1 track during the F1 Madrid Groundbreaking event\n', 729, 1296, '2025-04-28 00:18:43', '7f8d8e86fb336'),
	(3, 'Take a virtual lap of Madrid\'s new \'Madring\' circuit', 'Ride onboard for a virtual lap of the new \'Madring\' circuit, which will be the venue for the Spanish Grand Prix in 2026.', 'https://www.espn.com/video/clip?id=44851348', 'https://a.espncdn.com/media/motion/2025/0425/dm_250425_Take_a_virtual_lap_of_Madrids_new_Madring_circuit/dm_250425_Take_a_virtual_lap_of_Madrids_new_Madring_circuit.jpg', 'Ride onboard for a virtual lap of the new \'Madring\' circuit, which will be the venue for the Spanish Grand Prix in 2026.', '', 324, 576, '2025-04-28 00:18:43', 'b6385893c50da'),
	(4, 'Madrid Madring: F1 race organisers reveal track layout for 2026 Spanish Grand Prix', 'Organisers of Madrid\'s new Spanish Grand Prix venue have revealed the 22-corner circuit layout, including an extremely banked corner called \'La Monumental\'.', 'https://www.espn.co.uk/f1/story/_/id/44851193/f1-race-organisers-reveal-madrid-track-layout-2026-spanish-grand-prix', 'https://a.espncdn.com/photo/2025/0425/r1483789_608x342_16-9.png', '', '', 342, 608, '2025-04-28 00:18:43', '7dbdf33a71f63'),
	(5, 'How Hamilton helped Idris, Pitt bring \'F1\' movie to life', 'With real race cars and Lewis Hamilton advising, Damson Idris talks the realism of filming June\'s "F1" movie.', 'https://www.espn.com/racing/f1/story/_/id/44835305/how-lewis-hamilton-helped-damson-idris-brad-pitt-bring-f1-movie-life', 'https://a.espncdn.com/photo/2025/0424/r1483330_1296x729_16-9.jpg', 'Damson Idris', 'Damson Idris', 729, 1296, '2025-04-28 00:18:43', 'b6ac6a4c360c1'),
	(6, 'McLaren to leave Formula E at end of 2024-25 season', 'McLaren will leave the all-electric Formula E championship at the end of the 2024-25 season to focus on Formula 1, IndyCar and a new hypercar project from 2027 in the World Endurance Championship.', 'https://www.espn.co.uk/f1/story/_/id/44848944/mclaren-leave-formula-e-end-2024-25-season', 'https://a.espncdn.com/photo/2024/1018/r1402373_1296x729_16-9.jpg', '', 'McLaren Chief Executive Officer Zak Brown', 729, 1296, '2025-04-28 00:18:43', '015b57f92aac9'),
	(7, 'Jason Kidd joins athletes who became owners', 'The Dallas Mavericks coach joins a list of athletes that includes LeBron James, Serena Williams, Wayne Gretzky and Tom Brady.', 'https://www.espn.com/nfl/story/_/id/29553205/dwyane-wade-tom-brady-lebron-james-athletes-team-owners', 'https://a.espncdn.com/photo/2023/1027/r1244592_608x342_16-9.jpg', '', '', 342, 608, '2025-04-28 00:18:43', '14510466789c5'),
	(8, 'What it\'s like being trained by Lewis Hamilton', 'Actor Damson Idris speaks about what it was like having Lewis Hamilton as a mentor on set while filming the movie "F1".', 'https://www.espn.com/video/clip?id=44835583', 'https://a.espncdn.com/media/motion/2025/0424/dm_250424_COM_F1_Interview_What_its_like_being_trained_by_Lewis_Hamilton_GLOBAL_20250424/dm_250424_COM_F1_Interview_What_its_like_being_trained_by_Lewis_Hamilton_GLOBAL_20250424.jpg', 'Actor Damson Idris speaks about what it was like having Lewis Hamilton as a mentor on set while filming the movie "F1".', '', 324, 576, '2025-04-28 00:18:43', '3536e8a300855'),
	(9, 'EA Sports F1 25 preview: Aiming for the championships', 'Braking Point returns in EA F1 25, with new difficulty levels and a continuation of the game\'s story.', 'https://www.espn.com/gaming/story/_/id/44822392/ea-sports-f1-25-preview-braking-point', 'https://a.espncdn.com/photo/2025/0423/r1483003_1296x729_16-9.jpg', 'Konnersport is finally taking on the championships.', '', 729, 1296, '2025-04-28 00:18:43', '560e27b64ab4f'),
	(10, 'General Motors approved as F1 engine supplier for 2029 to power Cadillac', 'Formula 1\'s governing body, the FIA, has approved General Motors as an official power unit supplier from the 2029 season onwards.', 'https://www.espn.co.uk/f1/story/_/id/44818815/general-motors-approved-f1-engine-supplier-2029-power-cadillac', 'https://a.espncdn.com/photo/2024/1126/r1419999_1296x729_16-9.jpg', 'Cadillac F1', 'Cadillac F1', 729, 1296, '2025-04-28 00:18:43', '83ef0047a0632'),
	(11, 'Lewis Hamilton and Leonardo DiCaprio-backed burger chain to shut UK restaurants', 'The vegan burger chain backed by Lewis Hamilton and Leanardo DiCaprio is closing all of its UK restaurants, a spokesperson has confirmed to ESPN.', 'https://www.espn.co.uk/f1/story/_/id/44815019/lewis-hamilton-leonardo-dicaprio-backed-burger-chain-shut-uk-restaurants', 'https://a.espncdn.com/photo/2025/0413/r1478212_1296x729_16-9.jpg', '', 'Lewis Hamilton of Great Britain and Ferrari answers questions in the media pen during the F1 Grand Prix of Bahrain', 729, 1296, '2025-04-28 00:18:43', 'd7d7dbe639922'),
	(12, 'FIA: Rally boss Malcolm Wilson nominated for deputy president role', 'The head of motorsport\'s world governing body, the FIA, has nominated former rally driver and M-Sport founder Malcolm Wilson to take the position left vacant by fellow-Briton Robert Reid as deputy president for sport.', 'https://www.espn.co.uk/f1/story/_/id/44814382/rally-boss-malcolm-wilson-nominated-deputy-president-role', 'https://a.espncdn.com/photo/2025/0423/r1482747_800x450_16-9.jpg', 'Malcolm Wilson has been nominated by FIA president Mohammed Ben Sulayem for the vacant role as deputy president for sport.', '', 450, 800, '2025-04-28 00:18:43', '0b63ee77ca3e9'),
	(13, 'Rock stars of racing gather for the 2025 Miami Grand Prix', 'Tune in as the Formula 1 season continues in Miami on Sunday, May 4, on ABC.', 'https://www.espn.com/video/clip?id=44803676', 'https://a.espncdn.com/media/motion/2025/0422/dm_250422_Miami_Grand_Prix_Promo/dm_250422_Miami_Grand_Prix_Promo.jpg', 'Tune in as the Formula 1 season continues in Miami on Sunday, May 4, on ABC.', '', 324, 576, '2025-04-28 00:18:43', '20f9d08d0e7b8'),
	(14, 'Drivers, teams who need a reset after F1\'s first five races', 'It\'s been a whirlwind to start the F1 season, five races in six weekends, and these names could use a breather.', 'https://www.espn.com/racing/f1/story/_/id/44783191/drivers-teams-need-reset-f1-first-five-races', 'https://a.espncdn.com/photo/2025/0421/r1481849_1296x729_16-9.jpg', 'Lewis Hamilton and Lando Norris', 'Lewis Hamilton and Lando Norris', 729, 1296, '2025-04-28 00:18:43', 'd63f665002baf'),
	(15, 'Lando Norris to skip King\'s Day celebrations to focus on F1 title bid', 'Lando Norris has said he will not be attending King\'s Day in Amsterdam this year as he is concentrating on his bid to become Formula 1 world champion.', 'https://www.espn.co.uk/f1/story/_/id/44781749/lando-norris-skip-kings-day-celebrations-focus-f1-title-bid', 'https://a.espncdn.com/photo/2025/0421/r1481795_1296x729_16-9.jpg', '', 'Lando Norris of Great Britain and McLaren F1 nurses a cut on his nose following an incident in Amsterdam last week, during previews ahead of the F1 Grand Prix of Miami at Miami International Autodrome\n', 729, 1296, '2025-04-28 00:18:43', '9d616e27caa76'),
	(16, 'Saudi Arabian GP: Lando Norris says Ferrari, Red Bull \'just as quick\' as McLaren', 'Lando Norris pointed to Ferrari\'s speed in Saudi Arabia as proof that McLaren\'s car is not as dominant as some onlookers say.', 'https://www.espn.co.uk/f1/story/_/id/44780630/saudi-arabia-gp-lando-norris-says-ferrari-just-quick-mclaren-races', 'https://a.espncdn.com/photo/2025/0421/r1481762_1296x729_16-9.jpg', '', 'Lando Norris of Great Britain and McLaren walks in the paddock during the F1 Grand Prix of Saudi Arabia at Jeddah Corniche Circuit\n', 729, 1296, '2025-04-28 00:18:43', '240365509a066'),
	(17, 'Verstappen: Not allowed to express opinion on five-second penalty', 'Max Verstappen and Oscar Piastri reflect on the Saudi Arabian Grand Prix.', 'https://www.espn.com/video/clip?id=44778997', 'https://a.espncdn.com/media/motion/2025/0421/dm_250421_COM_F1_Interview_Verstappen_Not_allowed_to_express_opinion_on_five_second_penalty_GLOBAL_exclu/dm_250421_COM_F1_Interview_Verstappen_Not_allowed_to_express_opinion_on_five_second_penalty_GLOBAL_exclu.', 'Max Verstappen and Oscar Piastri reflect on the Saudi Arabian Grand Prix.', '', 324, 576, '2025-04-28 00:18:43', '8d923072a9c9b'),
	(18, 'How Piastri-Verstappen incident led to McLaren\'s Saudi win', 'After nearly colliding on Lap 1 Max Verstappen was forced to yield to eventual Saudi GP winner Oscar Piastri.', 'https://www.espn.com/racing/f1/story/_/id/44774829/how-oscar-piastri-max-verstappen-incident-led-mclaren-saudi-arabian-gp-f1-win', 'https://a.espncdn.com/photo/2025/0421/r1481689_1296x729_16-9.jpg', 'Max Verstappen and Oscar Piastri', 'Max Verstappen and Oscar Piastri', 729, 1296, '2025-04-28 00:18:43', '104c3a57cd1ba'),
	(19, 'Oscar Piastri makes history with victory at Saudi Arabian Grand Prix', 'The 23-year-old becomes the first Australian since 2010 to lead the Formula 1 Championship.', 'https://www.espn.com/video/clip?id=44774324', 'https://a.espncdn.com/media/motion/2025/0420/dm_250420_INET_Highlight_Oscar_Piastri_makes_history_with_victory_at_Saudi_Arabian_Grand_Prix_20240421_AUS/dm_250420_INET_Highlight_Oscar_Piastri_makes_history_with_victory_at_Saudi_Arabian_Grand_Prix_20240421_', 'The 23-year-old becomes the first Australian since 2010 to lead the Formula 1 Championship.', '', 324, 576, '2025-04-28 00:18:43', 'de3c824855910'),
	(20, 'Saudi Arabian GP: Lando Norris says fourth was best he could do', 'Lando Norris said there was nothing more he could do after finishing fourth in Sunday\'s Saudi Arabian Grand Prix and losing his Formula 1 championship lead to winning McLaren teammate Oscar Piastri.', 'https://www.espn.co.uk/f1/story/_/id/44771689/lando-norris-says-fourth-was-best-do', 'https://a.espncdn.com/photo/2025/0420/r1481593_800x450_16-9.jpg', '', 'Lando Norris of Great Britain and McLaren walks in the paddock during the F1 Grand Prix of Saudi Arabia at Jeddah Corniche Circuit', 450, 800, '2025-04-28 00:18:43', '0e6e590f1f9a0'),
	(21, 'McLaren\'s Oscar Piastri on top of the world after Saudi Arabian GP win', 'Oscar Piastri put Australia on top of the Formula 1 world championship for the first time since 2010 on Sunday but the McLaren driver said he was still a long way from where he wanted to be despite his Saudi Arabian Grand Prix victory.', 'https://www.espn.co.uk/f1/story/_/id/44771489/mclaren-oscar-piastri-top-world-saudi-arabian-gp-win', 'https://a.espncdn.com/photo/2025/0420/r1481472_800x450_16-9.jpg', '', 'McLaren\'s Australian driver Oscar Piastri celebrates winning the 2025 Saudi Arabia Formula One Grand Prix at the Jeddah Corniche Circuit', 450, 800, '2025-04-28 00:18:43', 'dd4a3c9baf8ce'),
	(22, 'Saudi Arabian GP: Max Verstappen says people can\'t handle \'full truth\' after penalty', 'Max Verstappen refused to offer his opinion on the decisive penalty that cost him victory at the Saudi Arabian Grand Prix, saying "people can\'t handle the full truth."', 'https://www.espn.co.uk/f1/story/_/id/44771004/max-verstappen-says-people-handle-truth-first-corner-incident', 'https://a.espncdn.com/photo/2025/0420/r1481587_800x450_16-9.jpg', '', 'Max Verstappen of the Netherlands and Oracle Red Bull Racing looks on on the grid during the F1 Grand Prix of Saudi Arabia at Jeddah Corniche Circuit', 450, 800, '2025-04-28 00:18:43', '96e39a0d40a90'),
	(23, 'Saudi Arabian GP: Lewis Hamilton says \'nothing positive\' to take from P7 result', 'A downbeat Lewis Hamilton said there was nothing positive to take from his seventh-place finish at the Saudi Arabian Grand Prix.', 'https://www.espn.co.uk/f1/story/_/id/44770602/lewis-hamilton-says-positive-take-p7-result', 'https://a.espncdn.com/photo/2025/0420/r1481556_800x450_16-9.jpg', '', 'Lewis Hamilton of Great Britain and Scuderia Ferrari arrives on the grid during the F1 Grand Prix of Saudi Arabia at Jeddah Corniche Circuit', 450, 800, '2025-04-28 00:18:43', 'c86044c7b6943'),
	(24, 'Leclerc: Nothing more on the table at Saudi Arabian Grand Prix', 'Charles Leclerc and Lando Norris reflect on the Saudi Arabian Grand Prix.', 'https://www.espn.com/video/clip?id=44770814', 'https://a.espncdn.com/media/motion/2025/0420/dm_250420_COM_F1_Analysis_Leclerc3A_Nothing_more_on_the_table_at_Saudi_Arabian_Grand_Prix_GLOBAL_2025-04-20/dm_250420_COM_F1_Analysis_Leclerc3A_Nothing_more_on_the_table_at_Saudi_Arabian_Grand_Prix_GLOBAL_2025-', 'Charles Leclerc and Lando Norris reflect on the Saudi Arabian Grand Prix.', '', 324, 576, '2025-04-28 00:18:43', '6b84fe3a24b8c'),
	(25, 'Oscar Piastri wins first Saudi Arabian GP', 'The numbers behind Oscar Piastri\'s fifth career victory at the Saudi Arabian Grand Prix.', 'https://www.espn.com/video/clip?id=44768986', 'https://a.espncdn.com/media/motion/2025/0420/dm_250420_COM_F1_Analysis_Oscar_Piastri_wins_first_Saudi_Arabian_GP_GLOBAL_2025-04-20/dm_250420_COM_F1_Analysis_Oscar_Piastri_wins_first_Saudi_Arabian_GP_GLOBAL_2025-04-20.jpg', 'The numbers behind Oscar Piastri\'s fifth career victory at the Saudi Arabian Grand Prix.', '', 324, 576, '2025-04-28 00:18:43', '87e1286411a84'),
	(26, 'Ayrton Senna helmet from famous 1992 rescue sells for record price', 'The helmet worn by Ayrton Senna during one of his most iconic Formula 1 acts at the 1992 Belgian Grand Prix has been sold for a record Â£720,000 ($966,449), auctioneers have said.', 'https://www.espn.co.uk/f1/story/_/id/44917570/ayrton-senna-helmet-famous-1992-rescue-sells-record-price', 'https://a.espncdn.com/photo/2025/0429/r1485638_1296x729_16-9.jpg', 'Ayrton Senna wore the helmet for much of the 1992 season, including at the 1992 Belgian Grand Prix', 'Ayrton Senna wore the helmet for much of the 1992 season, including at the 1992 Belgian Grand Prix', 729, 1296, '2025-04-30 12:11:38', '8c242c274eee7'),
	(27, 'FIA chief considering \'improvements\' to F1\'s swearing rules', 'Mohammed Ben Sulayem said on Monday he was considering "improvements" to rules that impose heavy sanctions for misconduct, including swearing, in F1.', 'https://www.espn.co.uk/f1/story/_/id/44914382/fia-chief-considering-improvements-f1-swearing-rules', 'https://a.espncdn.com/photo/2025/0429/r1485573_1296x729_16-9.jpg', '', 'Second placed Max Verstappen of the Netherlands and Oracle Red Bull Racing talks with Mohammed ben Sulayem, FIA President in parc ferme during the F1 Grand Prix of Saudi Arabia at Jeddah Corniche Circuit\n', 729, 1296, '2025-04-30 12:11:38', '71b283276269f'),
	(28, 'Why the Miami Grand Prix is huge for Lando Norris', 'Nate Saunders explains why the pressure is on for Lando Norris ahead of the Miami Grand Prix.', 'https://www.espn.com/video/clip?id=44951563', 'https://a.espncdn.com/media/motion/2025/0501/dm_250501_Why_the_Miami_Grand_Prix_is_huge_for_Lando_Norris/dm_250501_Why_the_Miami_Grand_Prix_is_huge_for_Lando_Norris.jpg', 'Nate Saunders explains why the pressure is on for Lando Norris ahead of the Miami Grand Prix.', '', 324, 576, '2025-05-01 20:45:21', 'a2873a47a95e1'),
	(29, 'Has Piastri shown the way to battle Verstappen on-track?', 'The "Unlapped" podcast team discuss the emerging on-track rivalry between Max Verstappen and Oscar Piastri.', 'https://www.espn.com/video/clip?id=44951486', 'https://a.espncdn.com/media/motion/2025/0501/dm_250501_Has_Piastri_shown_the_way_to_battle_Verstappen_on_track/dm_250501_Has_Piastri_shown_the_way_to_battle_Verstappen_on_track.jpg', 'The "Unlapped" podcast team discuss the emerging on-track rivalry between Max Verstappen and Oscar Piastri.', '', 324, 576, '2025-05-01 20:45:21', 'ef63ae6115156'),
