	(114, 'Cadillac confirm Sergio PÃ©rez, Valtteri Bottas for 2026 F1 debut', 'Cadillac has confirmed Sergio PÃ©rez and Valtteri Bottas will form its driver lineup for its Formula 1 debut season in 2026.', 'https://www.espn.co.uk/f1/story/_/id/46077362/cadillac-confirm-sergio-perez-valtteri-bottas-2026-f1-debut', 'https://a.espncdn.com/photo/2025/0826/r1536889_1296x729_16-9.jpg', 'Valtteri Bottas and Sergio PÃ©rez will form an experienced lineup at Cadillac next season.', 'Valtteri Bottas of Alfa Romeo and Sergio Perez of Red Bull Racing before the drivers parade ahead the Formula 1 Grand Prix of Canada at Circuit Gilles Villeneuve in Montreal, Canada on June 18, 2023.', 729, 1296, '2025-08-27 17:09:01', '6e1227ce626e1'),
